## Observations

The repository currently contains only `Patchive.md` — a product brief describing the full PatchHive ecosystem: an umbrella brand (`PatchHive`), a unified workspace (`HiveCore`), and 10 focused maintenance products. No code, framework, or tooling exists yet. The document includes hero copy, CTAs, positioning, and MVP scopes for each product, giving clear content direction for every site.

## Approach

Build a **monorepo of static marketing sites** — one per product plus the umbrella and HiveCore — using a shared design system. Each site follows the same page structure but with product-specific copy, color accent, and CTA. This keeps maintenance low and brand cohesion high.

