### Step 6 — Wire up routing and cross-linking

Ensure every site's `Nav` "All Products" dropdown links to all other product sites. Every `Footer` links back to `patchhive.dev` and includes the "Powered by HiveCore" badge. The umbrella site's product cards link to each product subdomain.

### Step 7 — Configure deployment

Set up one deployment target per app (e.g., Vercel projects or Netlify sites), mapping each app to its subdomain. Configure the monorepo build pipeline so a single CI run can build and deploy all sites, or deploy only changed apps on each push.